# Dependabot's root npm job pulls in every package.json in the repo (root +
# packages/code-reviewer) for resolution. code-reviewer's @openai/codex deps
# use npm:-aliased platform builds that Dependabot misclassifies as a private
# registry, erroring the whole npm run. Mapping the @openai scope to the public
# registry here (root is where Dependabot reads it for the / job) fixes it.
# Public packages only — no functional change to installs. Ref dependabot-core#13797.
@openai:registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
